        <item>
            <title>1.4.1</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 23:40:15 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>9</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.4.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Changes
- Add visual progress bars for 5-hour and weekly rate limit indicators in the status bar, matching the existing context usage bar style
- Rate limit data now updates more responsively by requesting updates on all CLI events (throttled to once per 60 seconds)

### Bug Fixes
- Fix ContentViewer crash when opening files from chat
- Restore `open_file` functionality that was broken by the shim migration
]]></description>
